'''Amazon Lumberyard'''是一款免费的跨平台[[AAA_(电子游戏产业)|3A]][[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]，是[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]在2015年获得[[Crytek|Crytek]]授权后，以[[CryEngine|CryEngine]]为基础构建而成<ref name="pcgamer">{{cite web | url=http://www.pcgamer.com/amazon-launches-free-triple-a-lumberyard-engine/ | title=Amazon launches free 'triple-A' Lumberyard engine | date=February 9, 2016 | accessdate=February 20, 2016 | website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | first=Angus | last=Morrison | archive-date=2017-01-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102073935/http://www.pcgamer.com/amazon-launches-free-triple-a-lumberyard-engine// | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gamespot">{{cite web | url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-and-crytek-agree-to-licensing-deal-worth-50/1100-6426438/ | title=Amazon and Crytek Agree to Licensing Deal Worth $50-$70 Million - Report | date=April 6, 2015 | accessdate=February 20, 2016 | website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | first=Eddie | last=Makuch | archive-date=2015-10-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008014324/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-and-crytek-agree-to-licensing-deal-worth-50/1100-6426438/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="venturebeat">{{cite web | url=http://venturebeat.com/2016/02/12/inside-amazons-decision-to-make-a-video-game-engine/ | title=Inside Amazon’s decision to make a video game engine | date=February 12, 2016 | accessdate=February 20, 2016 | last=Takahashi | first=Dean | website=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]] | archive-date=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019042811/http://venturebeat.com/2016/02/12/inside-amazons-decision-to-make-a-video-game-engine/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。该引擎与[[亞馬遜網路服務系統|亞馬遜網路服務系統]]（AWS）集成，允许开发人员在亚马逊的服务器上构建或托管他们的游戏，并且通过[[Twitch|Twitch]]来进行游戏直播<ref name="polygon">{{cite web | url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/2/9/10949002/amazon-lumberyard-free-games-engine/ | title=Amazon rolls out Lumberyard, an entirely free game development engine | date=February 9, 2016 | accessdate=February 20, 2016 | website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] | first=Owen S. | last=Good | archive-date=2016-12-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219184824/http://www.polygon.com/2016/2/9/10949002/amazon-lumberyard-free-games-engine | dead-url=no }}</ref>。亚马逊向最终用户免费提供Lumberyard引擎的源代码，但有一些限制：用户不能将源代码进行公开，或使用它来发布自己的游戏引擎<ref>{{Cite web|title = Amazon Lumberyard FAQ|url = https://aws.amazon.com/lumberyard/faq/|website = Amazon Web Services, Inc.|access-date = February 23, 2016|archive-date = 2016-12-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161210020109/https://aws.amazon.com/lumberyard/faq/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

Lumberyard于2016年2月9日与[[GameLift|GameLift]]一起推出<ref name="gamasutra">{{cite web | url=http://gamasutra.com/view/news/265425/Amazon_launches_new_free_highquality_game_engine_Lumberyard.php | title=Amazon launches new, free, high-quality game engine: Lumberyard | date=February 9, 2016 | accessdate=February 20, 2016 | website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | first=Christian | last=Nutt | archive-date=2016-12-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203201012/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/265425/Amazon_launches_new_free_highquality_game_engine_Lumberyard.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>。该引擎目前处于测试阶段，可用于构建[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]平台上的游戏<ref name="kotaku">{{cite web | url=http://kotaku.com/amazon-releases-its-own-game-engine-for-free-1757995787 | title=Amazon Releases Its Own Game Engine For Free | date=February 9, 2016 | accessdate=February 20, 2016 | website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | first=András | last=Neltz | archive-date=2016-12-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161212105632/http://kotaku.com/amazon-releases-its-own-game-engine-for-free-1757995787 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gamasutra" />，对[[iOS|iOS]]和[[Android|Android]]平台提供有限的支持<ref name="update11">{{cite web |url=https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/gamedev/now-available-lumberyard-beta-1-1-2/ |title=Now Available – Lumberyard Beta 1.1 |website=Amazon GameDev Blog |date=March 14, 2016 |first=J.C. |last=Connors |accessdate=April 2, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130121144/https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/gamedev/now-available-lumberyard-beta-1-1-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

亚马逊于2016年3月14日发布了对Lumberyard的更新，其中包括对某些移动设备的支持（如基于[[Apple_A8|A8处理器]]的iOS设备和[[Nvidia_Shield|Nvidia Shield]]），对{{link-en|FBX|FBX}}（'''F'''ilm'''b'''o'''x'''，[[Autodesk|Autodesk]]旗下[[电子游戏|游戏]][[中间件|中间件]]所用文件格式）的支持，以及与Allegorithmic的纹理化软件Substance进行了集成<ref name="update11" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.develop-online.net/news/first-amazon-lumberyard-update-brings-mobile-support-substance-integration/0218013 |title=First Amazon Lumberyard update brings mobile support, Substance integration |website=[[Develop_(magazine)|Develop]] |publisher=NewBay Media |date=March 16, 2016 |first=Matthew |last=Jarvis |accessdate=April 2, 2016 |archive-date=2016-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702055630/http://www.develop-online.net/news/first-amazon-lumberyard-update-brings-mobile-support-substance-integration/0218013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

